Klasse GraphicsPipeline.GraphicsPipelineInfo

java.lang.Object
Kartoffel.Licht.Vulkan.GraphicsPipeline.GraphicsPipelineInfo
Umschließende Klasse:
GraphicsPipeline
public static class GraphicsPipeline.GraphicsPipelineInfo extends Object
Holds information about the Graphics pipeline. All components included.
